<section sectnbr = "7B">
<servcat sctnbr = "07" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "2">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B7226009" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
HVAC Unit Removal and Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B7226008">HVAC Unit Components:Manual Type</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B7226016">Evaporator Temperature Sensor Inspection:Manual Type</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B7226009001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disable air bag system. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B8206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Recover refrigerant from A/C system using recovery and recycling equipment referring to “Recovery” in 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B7226001">Operation Procedure for Refrigerant Charge:Manual Type</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drain engine coolant. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B1606004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Then disconnect heater hoses from HVAC unit.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove cowl top garnish. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B9806005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Loosen bolt (1), then remove liquid pipe and suction hose from expansion valve (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V20A720023.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "41.377mm" ver = "01" gw = "98" gh = "101"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove instrument panel from vehicle body. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove HVAC unit (1) from vehicle body by removing nuts (2).
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
When removing HVAC unit, be careful not to spill engine coolant and compressor oil on vehicle floor.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A721018.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "77.963mm" ver = "01" gw = "231" gh = "204"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B7226009002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B7226014">Evaporator Inspection:Manual Type</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B7226015">Evaporator Temperature Sensor Removal and Installation:Manual Type</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure, noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Replenish A/C compressor with compressor oil to specified amount from compressor suction side referring to “Replenishing Compressor Oil” in 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B7226001">Operation Procedure for Refrigerant Charge:Manual Type</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Install padding (1) to installation hole uniformly.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A721025.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.129mm" ver = "02" gw = "154" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Evacuate and charge the A/C system referring to “Evacuation” and “Charge” in 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B7226001">Operation Procedure for Refrigerant Charge:Manual Type</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Refill cooling system with coolant. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B1606006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Adjust control cables. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B7226020"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
